data.description: Recently updated luxury townhome located in the sought-after Walnut Creek community. The entire residence has been refreshed with a new coat of paint, providing a clean and inviting atmosphere. The main level offers a bright and open space, seamlessly connecting the gourmet chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line fixtures to a cozy living room, a full dining area, and a convenient work nook. Charm brought to life by recessed lighting and stylish LVP flooring throughout. Upstairs, discover a versatile loft. The oversized primary bedroom boasts an attached en-suite with 2 closets, adding a touch of luxury. Two additional bedrooms offer flexibility or a private office. Step outside to a fenced yard and patio. The Walnut Creek community offers an array of amenities, including two expansive pools, a splash zone, walking trails, a recreation field, playgrounds, and a clubhouse. Don't miss the chance to make this beautifully updated townhome yours!
